article_title: Obamacare Startup Oscar Health Hits A $1.5 Billion Valuation

article_metadata.description: Some of tech's top investors think Oscar Health is just what the doctor ordered. Today, the New York health insurance start-up announced it raised $145 million dollars in a Series B round. The Oscar team would not comment on valuation, but sources close to the deal said the funding values Oscar [...]
